                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-936-18651023 t18651023-936-punishment-20"></join>Ten Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">The deficiencies attributable to the prisoners amounted to </hi>500<hi rend="italic">l. There were other indictments against them—(See Fourth Court, Wednesday.</hi>)</p>
